---
title: Beef Meatball 'Banh Mi' & Sriracha Mayo with Celery Slaw & Fries
description: Inspired by the loveable Vietnamese sub, this version will take you to the streets of Hanoi on the first bite.
Smear over a sriracha mayo and pack in some sweet and soy beef meatballs to balance out a peppery sesame slaw. To add something a bit different, serve with a side of fries to dip in some garlic aioli.
